    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo registers and documents the 'haptics' top-level media type, under which subtypes for representation formats for haptics may be registered.  This document also serves as a registration for a set of subtypes, which are representative of some existing subtypes already in use.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
